    "body" : "<p>Answering an old and accepted question here. You can add this in your pom.xml if you want to avoid passing command line argument all the time:</p>\n<pre><code>  &lt;properties&gt;\n      &lt;skipTests&gt;true&lt;/skipTests&gt;\n  &lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
