    "answer_id" : 26517375,
    "question_id" : 7456006,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>&lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;maven.test.skip&gt;true&lt;/maven.test.skip&gt;\n&lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>is also a way to add in pom file</p>\n"
  }, {
