    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 13,
    "last_activity_date" : 1538015345,
    "creation_date" : 1538015345,
    "answer_id" : 52528542,
    "question_id" : 7456006,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can add either <code>-DskipTests</code> or <code>-Dmaven.test.skip=true</code> to any <code>mvn</code> command for skipping tests. In your case it would be like below:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn package -DskipTests\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn package -Dmaven.test.skip=true\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
