    "answer_id" : 52866673,
    "question_id" : 7456006,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For maven package without infecting maven test:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;maven.test.failure.ignore&gt;true&lt;/maven.test.failure.ignore&gt;\n&lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
